            <title>三星從 2025 年起支援 Qi2 無線充電，Galaxy S25 首發？</title>
            <description>&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;Samsung 從 2025 年起支援 Qi2 無線充電，Galaxy S25 首發？&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-01/8dd87870-ccac-11ef-bfb6-1fbac84b693f&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;Samsung 從 2025 年起支援 Qi2 無線充電，Galaxy S25 首發？&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:1;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20250106397777/en/Qi2%E2%80%99s-Wireless-Charging-Benefits-Spurring-Continued-Expansion&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:無線充電聯盟;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;無線充電聯盟&lt;/a&gt;最新的資料顯示，三星的 Galaxy 手機將從 2025 年起支援 Qi2 無線充電。根據最初的願景，Qi2 早該為 Android 裝置帶來 iPhone MagSafe 式的便利，但大多數 Android 廠商在 2024 年並沒什麼實質性的動作。這種情況在 2025 年可望迎來改變，除了明確表態將推出相關產品的三星外，Google 也有「把自己的高功率無線充電技術貢獻給無線充電聯盟以開發 Qi v2.2」，這不免會讓人對未來的 Pixel 有所期待。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container caas-img-loader&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img caas-lazy has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;Galaxy S25 Spigen Crystal Flex&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-01/ab51ca00-ccac-11ef-af77-13df5bedc094&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;Galaxy S25 Spigen Crystal Flex&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;至於最先用上 Qi2 的 Android 硬體，很有可能會是即將於 1 月 23 日凌晨發表的 Galaxy S25。早先有 Spigen 的 S25 保護殼流出，上面已出現了類似 iPhone 官方磁吸配件的標誌性圓環呢。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;緊貼最新科技資訊、網購優惠，追隨 Yahoo Tech 各大社交平台！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech Facebook：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:2;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech Instagram：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:3;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 社羣：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:4;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 頻道：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:5;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech Telegram 頻道：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:6;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://t.me/yahootechhk&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://